## Modify // Center Window // <><Alt> c ##
bindsym $mod+$alt+c [con_id="__focused__"] move position center

## Modify // Window Sticky Toggle // <><Shift> s ##
bindsym $mod+Shift+s sticky toggle

## Modify // Border Toggle // <> b ##
bindsym $mod+b border toggle

## Launch // Workrave Rest Break // <><Alt> b ##
bindsym $mod+$alt+b exec --no-startup-id dbus-send --type=method_call --dest=org.workrave.Workrave /org/workrave/Workrave/UI org.workrave.ControlInterface.RestBreak
